data.description: This home includes 4 large bedrooms, eat in kitchen, side deck, and covered front porch great for sitting. Crawl space has storage room with cemented floor. Home features new HVAC system and duct work installed in 2021 and hot water heater installed in 2022. Seller states that there has been a recent remodel to the property and the following has been updated in the last 1.5 years: carpet, tile, window screens, insulation, and cabinets. Main bathroom has walk in shower. Refrigerator, washer, and dryer are included with the sale of the house.
